@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hrbehe(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((v0 / wp.cos(v1 + 0.58)) + (0.63 + v2))
    v2 = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.08 * v1 + 0.04)) - wp.exp((v2 + 0.45 - v1 + 0.69)))
    v0 = v0
    tmp = 0.18
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.abs(v2))
    data[tid] = v0
